overrideValues.value: SK8 is one of the most responsible companies I have ever seen. During the 3 months project collaborating with them, the Director Jack and other staff are professional and patient. I am not a technical person,  I just want to say they shine my eyes for what they did for me. Great company that I will always keep contact with!
